strings: <voice_0x01001744><se_def>the prince carlos: How can a careless cleaner get into trouble? Rotten trash!
<voice_0x01001745><se_def>the prince carlos: I should have known better than to reluctantly let the soldiers rescue the princess.
<voice_0x01001746><se_low>the key: So why not follow them and become a princess?
<voice_0x01001747><se_def>the prince carlos: But, but... well... I can't do it alone. I sent the emperor's coffin...
<voice_0x01001748><se_low>the key: You generals don't think that just because you're a prince you can decide everything with money and power.
<voice_0x01001749><se_def>the prince carlos: But at first he had a huge slow heart... one!
